&lt;section id="the-final-product" class="level2"&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;The Final Product&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The initial POV that inspired our design was: &lt;strong&gt;High school aged students getting ready for college need spaces away from home and school to help perform well in his studies.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our simulation proved that even college-level students have trouble completing relatively basic assignments in environments that aren’t conducive to learning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We observed that for every participant, more questions were successfully answered in the final quiet space we designed — they were able to complete problems without interruption and distraction!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
